subject: Greetings
body:
Greetings        
Auditors discovered in their 2023 Audit exceptions that your
Compensated COVID 19 fund is yet to be received by you.Please
respond as your funds and its accruing interest cannot remain in the
Government Sundry Suspense Account otherwise your efforts will be in
vain. Reply to my Private email: 
ry3965635@gmail.com
Regards
Barrister Michael Jenson
Debt Reconciliation Committee

subject: Re:    Greetings
body:
Greetings Barrister Michael Jenson,

Thank you for reaching out to me regarding the COVID fund. I appreciate your concern and would like to know more about the situation. Could you please provide me with some additional information? Specifically, I would like to understand why the funds have not been received yet and what steps need to be taken to ensure they are properly allocated.

Additionally, I would like to know more about the Audit exceptions that were discovered. What were these exceptions and how do they impact the release of the funds? It is important for me to have a clear understanding of the situation before proceeding further.

I look forward to your response and appreciate your assistance in resolving this matter.

Best wishes,
Shirlee
